OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FThe number of police-recorded
OL,7,Fshoplifting offences have hit a 20-
OL,8,Fyear high across England and Wales.
OL,10,FPolice forces logged a total of
OL,11,F443,995 instances in the year up to
OL,12,FMarch 2024. That is up 30% on the year
OL,13,Fprevious, from 342,428.
OL,15,FThe figure is at its highest level
OL,16,Fsince current records began in March
OL,17,F2003, according to the Office for
OL,18,FNational Statistics (ONS), which
OL,19,Fdescribed the latest increases as
OL,20,F"notable".
