OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FRetailers have been increasingly
OL,7,Fconcerned about the rising cost of
OL,8,Ftheft. Figures earlier this year
OL,9,Fshowed shoplifting was already at a 20-
OL,10,Fyear high, the latest figures show
OL,11,Fthat it has risen further.
OL,13,FShoplifters wielding machetes target a
OL,14,FCo-op store in Yorkshire last year
OL,16,FIn the wake of growing crime
OL,17,Fstatistics, the new Labour government
OL,18,Fhas vowed to tackle low-level
OL,19,Fshoplifting and make assaulting a shop
OL,20,Fworker a specific criminal offence.
