OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FThe move follows a long-running bid
OL,7,Ffrom business owners and Tory
OL,8,Fbackbencher Matt Vickers amid rising
OL,9,Fviolence against retail workers.
OL,11,FRetailers hope the measures set out
OL,12,Flast week in the King's Speech to
OL,13,FParliament will make it easier for
OL,14,Fpolice to investigate and prosecute
OL,15,Fcriminals.
OL,17,FThe figures also show the number of
OL,18,Foffences involving theft from the
OL,19,Fperson stood at 131,453 in 2023/24, up
OL,20,F17% from 112,225 in 2022/23.
