OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FThe number of robberies recorded rose
OL,7,Fby 8% to 81,019, up from 75,012 in the
OL,8,Fprevious 12 months ` though this
OL,9,Fremains below pre-pandemic levels,
OL,10,Fwith 90,198 offences in the year to
OL,11,FMarch 2020.
OL,13,FThere was a "notable increase" in the
OL,14,Fnumber of robberies involving a knife
OL,15,For sharp instrument, with 21,226
OL,16,Frecorded by forces in 2023/24, up 13%
OL,17,Ffrom 18,787 in the previous 12 months,
OL,18,Fthough this is below the 22,727 in
OL,19,F2019/20.
