OL,3,CShoplifting offences in England and
OL,4,CWales hit a 20-year high
OL,6,FOffences involving possession of an
OL,7,Farticle with a blade or point fell
OL,8,Fslightly to 27,470, down 3% from
OL,9,F28,391 in the previous 12 months.
OL,11,FThis follows "substantial increases in
OL,12,Frecent years, which may have been
OL,13,Finfluenced by targeted police action
OL,14,Fto tackle knife crime", the ONS said.
OL,16,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said the
OL,17,Ffigures represent "the appalling
OL,18,Flegacy of the Conservative government
OL,19,Fon law and order".
