OL,6,FShe added: "We have soaring
OL,7,Fshoplifting and soaring street crime
OL,8,Fhappening at a time when we have
OL,9,Fplummeting neighbourhood police."
OL,11,FPromising to put more police on the
OL,12,Fstreets, Ms Cooper emphasised the need
OL,13,Ffor people "to feel safe on the
OL,14,Fstreets."
